  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK490">
<l>kokkokka kūmpum paruvattu maṟṟataṉ</l>
<l>kuttokka cīrtta viṭattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>At the time when one should use self-control, let him restrain himself like a heron; and, let him like it, strike, when there is a favourable opportunity.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
